OL,3,CInquest into death of mother from
OL,4,Csickle cell disease looks at hospital
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FAn inquest into the death of a woman
OL,8,Ffrom sickle cell disease at Frimley
OL,9,FPark Hospital in Surrey opened today.
OL,10,FIrene Dzifa King Arthur from Church
OL,11,FCrookham in Hampshire died in August
OL,12,F2024 - following four days of care at
OL,13,Fthe Surrey hospital.
OL,15,FDuring the inquest her family raised
OL,16,Fconcerns about how her condition was
OL,17,Fmanaged at Frimley Park.
