OL,7,FThe inquest today (Tuesday 27 January)
OL,8,Ffocused on the medical care Irene
OL,9,Freceived in the days leading up to her
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FIrene Jeefer King Arthur was 47, a
OL,13,Fmother of two, and she had sickle cell
OL,14,Fdisease.
OL,16,FShe managed periods of pain at home,
OL,17,Fbut in August 2024 she was admitted to
OL,18,FFrimley Park Hospital where she died a
OL,19,Ffew days later.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
