OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FA post-mortem revealed the cause of
OL,8,Fher death as pulmonary emboli, or
OL,9,Fblood clots, together with her sickle
OL,10,Fcell disease and a virus she'd picked
OL,11,Fup, parvovirus.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday a witness statement was
OL,14,Fread out from Irene's husband Dominic.
OL,16,FIn it he said he'd spent time with his
OL,17,Fwife in hospital and said she told him
OL,18,Fshe felt she wasn't being listened to
OL,19,Fand he was worried about the level of
OL,20,Fknowledge of sickle cell disease.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
