OL,4,Csickle cell disease looks at hospital
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FA lot of the evidence surrounded a
OL,8,Fblood transfusion given to Irene on 7
OL,9,Fof August.
OL,11,FHer condition had deteriorated and
OL,12,Fquestions were asked about whether an
OL,13,Fearlier transfusion could have led to
OL,14,Fa different outcome.
OL,16,FDr Lucinda Blake, the consultant
OL,17,Fhaematologist at Frimley Park at the
OL,18,Ftime, said tests were regularly being
OL,19,Fcarried out and Irene had been moved
OL,20,Fcloser to the nurse's station for
OL,21,Fmonitoring.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
