OL,7,FShe was also successful in her career
OL,8,Fas an aviation policy advisor and she
OL,9,Fheld a position with a charity helping
OL,10,Fpeople with Downs Syndrome and their
OL,11,Ffamilies.
OL,13,FHer husband said the world was "a
OL,14,Fbetter place with her in it."
OL,16,FThe inquest into her death continues.
